Privacy Policy
Global Stock Systems Ltd built the OrderMe app as a commercial app to interface to the Samtouch POS Solution. This SERVICE is provided by Global Stock Systems Ltd and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform users of our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information for anyone who has chosen to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation with this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
This app can optionally utilise the camera in order to read user registration data in the form of a QR code. The images captured by the camera are processed entirely within the device and are not retained after processing.
In order to provide the Service, the app will requests signed using the registration data to the SamTouchOffice Back Office Solution. SamTouchOffice will return information relating to the sales, stock and other business information relating the tenants associated to the registration details.
The app does use third party services that may collect information used to identify you. The app is distributed via the Google Play Store and Google's Privacy Policy can be accessed by clicking
here.
